  "title": "Events sales & Marketing",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for an ambitious Events Sales & Marketing Executive (Entry Level) to help us increase our clients‘ Brand awareness and Customer base through the promotion of their products and services at our event sites in Singapore.</p><p><br /><u><strong>What You'll Do?</strong></u></p><p>- Participate and ensure the successful execution of our events marketing campaigns</p><p>- Promote our products or services to existing and potential customers</p><p>- Work with the rest of the marketing team to develop promotion strategies and oversee their implementation</p><p><br /><u><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></u></p><p>- Fast tracked career progression/growth</p><p>- Uncapped income</p><p>- Traveling opportunities</p><p>- 1-on-1 coaching / mentorship</p><p><br /><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><p>- Strong interpersonal and communications skills.</p><p>- Sales, customer service or events marketing experience is a plus.</p><p>- Strong organizational and project management skills.</p><p>- Attention to detail and ability to multi-task.</p><p>- Bachelor’s degree in Marketing, Business, or related field is a plus.</p>",
